1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,440 --> 00:01:42,310
[I Don't Want to be Friends With You]

3
00:01:52,900 --> 00:01:55,570
Why do we move so frequently?

4
00:01:56,460 --> 00:01:57,360
My goodness.

5
00:01:59,100 --> 00:01:59,979
Because

6
00:02:00,180 --> 00:02:02,120
we are near the Affiliated Primary School
of Normal University.

7
00:02:02,650 --> 00:02:04,610
Studying in this school
is not an easy thing.

8
00:02:04,700 --> 00:02:06,690
Living here can save a lot of trouble.

9
00:02:07,340 --> 00:02:09,210
We often move and I often
transfer to a new school

10
00:02:09,300 --> 00:02:11,290
so I have no friends.

11
00:02:12,500 --> 00:02:13,810
Li Jin Bu.

12
00:02:14,300 --> 00:02:15,960
Are you going to school to study

13
00:02:16,220 --> 00:02:17,810
or to make friends?

14
00:02:17,900 --> 00:02:18,840
I tell you that

15
00:02:18,930 --> 00:02:21,090
you should study hard in school.

16
00:02:21,180 --> 00:02:22,490
Only if you study hard

17
00:02:22,570 --> 00:02:24,050
can you get into a good college.

18
00:02:24,140 --> 00:02:24,810
Got it?

19
00:02:24,890 --> 00:02:26,930
Have you entered a good college?

20
00:02:28,820 --> 00:02:29,770
Me?

21
00:02:30,930 --> 00:02:32,120
At that time,

22
00:02:32,420 --> 00:02:34,570
no one offered such an opportunity for me

23
00:02:34,660 --> 00:02:35,760
and nobody

24
00:02:35,860 --> 00:02:37,170
supervised me.

25
00:02:37,300 --> 00:02:39,570
If I have a chance to be a teenager again,

26
00:02:39,820 --> 00:02:40,930
I must study hard

27
00:02:41,020 --> 00:02:42,690
and get into a good college.

28
00:02:45,380 --> 00:02:46,260
Li Jin Bu,

29
00:02:46,420 --> 00:02:48,000
I am talking to you.

30
00:02:48,090 --> 00:02:48,300
Don't go!

31
00:02:48,300 --> 00:02:48,740
[Episode 5: I Decide How You Study]

32
00:02:48,740 --> 00:02:50,329
Come to help me!

33
00:02:55,980 --> 00:02:56,860
Here you are.

34
00:03:01,380 --> 00:03:02,260
What are you going to do?

35
00:03:02,780 --> 00:03:04,160
This one's for her kicking you.

36
00:03:07,250 --> 00:03:08,570
She stole your check
and made you get scolded.

37
00:03:08,660 --> 00:03:09,880
This one is for that.

38
00:03:13,060 --> 00:03:14,250
Not enough?

39
00:03:17,130 --> 00:03:18,450
Then I'll slap myself
until you are satisfied.

40
00:03:23,620 --> 00:03:24,500
That's enough.

41
00:03:29,300 --> 00:03:30,290
God.

42
00:03:30,780 --> 00:03:32,090
I didn't expect this!

43
00:03:32,260 --> 00:03:34,290
She's a tough one!

44
00:04:14,370 --> 00:04:16,240
What's wrong with Hua?

45
00:04:16,450 --> 00:04:17,529
I don't know.

46
00:04:19,260 --> 00:04:20,519
Then what's wrong with Li Qing Tong ?

47
00:04:20,660 --> 00:04:21,959
I don't know, either.

48
00:04:53,540 --> 00:04:56,650
[Aurora Cool Play]

49
00:04:59,900 --> 00:05:00,360
Bro,

50
00:05:00,450 --> 00:05:01,610
I don't understand that

51
00:05:01,770 --> 00:05:03,210
it's just kidding to write
several words on her bag

52
00:05:03,300 --> 00:05:04,650
which can be cleaned up,

53
00:05:04,740 --> 00:05:06,450
why did you buy her a new one?

54
00:05:07,170 --> 00:05:08,370
There are so many things
you don't understand.

55
00:05:08,460 --> 00:05:09,770
Do I need to explain to you?

56
00:05:10,370 --> 00:05:11,970
What a shame for us then!

57
00:05:12,060 --> 00:05:13,290
First, we got kicked by a girl,

58
00:05:13,380 --> 00:05:14,880
then we apologised and made compensation.

59
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:16,330
Since we entered the
No.3 Middle School of Tieyuan

60
00:05:16,410 --> 00:05:17,890
we have never been in such a mess.

61
00:05:21,300 --> 00:05:22,180
What did you mean?

62
00:05:22,660 --> 00:05:23,540
Niu Xiao Huo.

63
00:05:25,010 --> 00:05:26,960
You think I embarrassed you?

64
00:05:27,140 --> 00:05:28,010
No.

65
00:05:28,090 --> 00:05:29,080
I didn't mean that.

66
00:05:29,170 --> 00:05:30,370
I was afraid you would be offended.

67
00:05:30,460 --> 00:05:31,500
Come, you come here.

68
00:05:31,590 --> 00:05:32,010
No, no, no.

69
00:05:32,100 --> 00:05:32,510
Bro, bro, bro.

70
00:05:32,590 --> 00:05:33,290
You are angry.

71
00:05:33,370 --> 00:05:33,920
Bro, you are angry.

72
00:05:34,010 --> 00:05:34,650
I can't deal with those girls,

73
00:05:34,740 --> 00:05:35,810
but I can deal with you.

74
00:05:35,890 --> 00:05:36,810
Bro.

75
00:05:37,210 --> 00:05:37,730
I...

76
00:05:37,820 --> 00:05:39,370
I am sorry.

77
00:05:47,380 --> 00:05:49,130
What did you say to him?

78
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:52,450
Life.

79
00:05:52,540 --> 00:05:53,190
Youth.

80
00:05:53,270 --> 00:05:54,260
Future.

81
00:05:54,590 --> 00:05:56,440
I have explained everything to him.

82
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,409
He even apologized to me.

83
00:05:59,330 --> 00:06:00,640
He apologized to you?

84
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:02,640
Sure.

85
00:06:03,140 --> 00:06:05,800
You have seen he bought a new bag for me.

86
00:06:06,460 --> 00:06:07,370
Life.

87
00:06:07,460 --> 00:06:08,250
Youth.

88
00:06:08,340 --> 00:06:09,210
Future.

89
00:06:09,300 --> 00:06:11,320
I hope you two can
really talk about these.

90
00:06:12,650 --> 00:06:13,570
What do you mean?

91
00:06:15,290 --> 00:06:16,050
Li Qing Tong.

92
00:06:16,140 --> 00:06:17,370
Forget about it this time.

93
00:06:17,460 --> 00:06:18,890
You are not allowed to associate
with such people in the future

94
00:06:18,980 --> 00:06:20,010
and better not to say a word.

95
00:06:20,100 --> 00:06:20,980
Understand?

96
00:06:21,500 --> 00:06:22,380
Understand.

97
00:06:23,850 --> 00:06:25,720
I wish we didn't have to
see each other anymore.

98
00:06:28,140 --> 00:06:29,800
Then I'll reward you with a break today.

99
00:06:31,130 --> 00:06:32,530
So can I go watch TV now?

100
00:06:32,740 --> 00:06:34,080
Only if you finish one test paper.

101
00:06:39,540 --> 00:06:40,480
Eat quickly!

102
00:06:41,130 --> 00:06:42,010
Have some food, Hua.

103
00:06:42,450 --> 00:06:44,000
Go back after dinner and
apologize to your mother.

104
00:06:45,180 --> 00:06:45,440
Hua.

105
00:06:45,530 --> 00:06:46,960
You say something nice to your aunt.

106
00:06:47,900 --> 00:06:48,850
Why do I apologize?

107
00:06:48,940 --> 00:06:50,130
I didn't make any mistakes.

108
00:06:51,300 --> 00:06:52,680
Whether you made a mistake or not,

109
00:06:52,860 --> 00:06:53,650
she was so angry

110
00:06:53,740 --> 00:06:55,490
and you should coax her.

111
00:06:56,700 --> 00:06:57,760
Mr Li.

112
00:06:58,180 --> 00:07:00,650
You are at least the head of the family.

113
00:07:00,930 --> 00:07:02,210
Why couldn't you have a sense of justice

114
00:07:02,300 --> 00:07:03,290
and redress the scales?

115
00:07:03,370 --> 00:07:05,490
You allow her to hector at home every day.

116
00:07:06,140 --> 00:07:07,370
How can I do this?

117
00:07:07,860 --> 00:07:09,890
If I do this I will be
beaten up by your mother.

118
00:07:10,850 --> 00:07:12,650
In our family your mother is justice.

119
00:07:12,740 --> 00:07:13,850
Why?

120
00:07:13,980 --> 00:07:14,810
Because she is your mother

121
00:07:14,900 --> 00:07:16,000
and my wife.

122
00:07:16,540 --> 00:07:17,420
You are afraid of your wife!

123
00:07:17,770 --> 00:07:18,530
You are right.

124
00:07:18,620 --> 00:07:19,610
I am afraid of my wife.

125
00:07:19,700 --> 00:07:21,400
Everyone in our factory
know that I am afraid of my wife.

126
00:07:21,700 --> 00:07:23,010
I am afraid of my own wife.

127
00:07:23,100 --> 00:07:24,530
Why can't I admit it?

128
00:07:27,570 --> 00:07:28,760
Why didn't you

129
00:07:28,890 --> 00:07:30,610
find a soft girlfriend in those days?

130
00:07:31,970 --> 00:07:34,210
Now you have to be scolded at home.

131
00:07:35,540 --> 00:07:37,920
You think I'm really
afraid of your mother?

132
00:07:38,010 --> 00:07:39,240
That's because of love!

133
00:07:39,500 --> 00:07:41,080
When I was at my poorest,

134
00:07:41,180 --> 00:07:42,370
your mother married me.

135
00:07:42,460 --> 00:07:44,960
Only I know how much she suffered.

136
00:07:45,420 --> 00:07:47,010
So at present, I, Li Wu Si,

137
00:07:47,100 --> 00:07:48,290
must protect her.

138
00:07:48,370 --> 00:07:50,170
As long as I am in this world,

139
00:07:50,770 --> 00:07:51,530
no matter when,

140
00:07:51,620 --> 00:07:52,610
no one can bully her,

141
00:07:52,700 --> 00:07:53,580
including you.

142
00:07:54,220 --> 00:07:56,450
Then your wife can bully me.

143
00:07:56,730 --> 00:07:57,770
You can only see your wife.

144
00:07:57,860 --> 00:07:59,890
Your daughter was picked
up from the garbage can.

145
00:08:00,300 --> 00:08:01,930
How can you say that, my sweetie?

146
00:08:02,010 --> 00:08:03,120
I need to protect her first,

147
00:08:03,210 --> 00:08:04,690
and then I can protect you.

148
00:08:05,780 --> 00:08:07,210
You are growing up,

149
00:08:07,290 --> 00:08:09,010
and you will have a husband in the future.

150
00:08:09,370 --> 00:08:10,810
Will you live with your husband?

151
00:08:10,900 --> 00:08:12,890
Only your mother can accompany
me for the rest of my life.

152
00:08:12,980 --> 00:08:14,810
If I don't protect her,
who will I protect?

153
00:08:15,380 --> 00:08:16,260
Ok, ok, ok.

154
00:08:16,970 --> 00:08:17,960
You two are in love.

155
00:08:18,610 --> 00:08:19,690
I'm on my own.

156
00:08:20,780 --> 00:08:21,660
Li Qing Tong.

157
00:08:22,250 --> 00:08:23,680
I'm not happy to hear that.

158
00:08:23,890 --> 00:08:25,120
Thinking about your mother,

159
00:08:25,890 --> 00:08:28,010
she took care of everything
when you grew up.

160
00:08:28,090 --> 00:08:29,400
I can say that

161
00:08:30,220 --> 00:08:31,230
whether you have your father

162
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:32,570
doesn't matter.

163
00:08:32,659 --> 00:08:33,570
But without your mother,

164
00:08:33,659 --> 00:08:34,730
you have nothing.

165
00:08:39,730 --> 00:08:41,600
I know she loves me,

166
00:08:42,380 --> 00:08:44,360
but the way she show it is wrong.

167
00:08:44,660 --> 00:08:45,170
Look,

168
00:08:45,250 --> 00:08:47,090
although the way is important,

169
00:08:47,180 --> 00:08:49,170
it's also your mother's first time
being a mother.

170
00:08:49,260 --> 00:08:50,170
She needs to have a

171
00:08:50,260 --> 00:08:52,160
process of adaptation.

172
00:08:53,050 --> 00:08:54,250
What I want to say is

173
00:08:54,810 --> 00:08:55,330
you need to think that

174
00:08:55,420 --> 00:08:57,130
all these years what did your mother

175
00:08:57,220 --> 00:08:58,570
do for you?

176
00:08:58,660 --> 00:08:59,540
Let's put it this way.

177
00:09:00,260 --> 00:09:01,490
When your mother was sick,

178
00:09:01,740 --> 00:09:02,640
did you just

179
00:09:02,730 --> 00:09:03,890
give some greetings

180
00:09:04,490 --> 00:09:06,450
and go back to your
room and sleep soundly?

181
00:09:06,780 --> 00:09:07,660
On the contrary,

182
00:09:08,100 --> 00:09:09,230
let alone when you're sick,

183
00:09:09,320 --> 00:09:10,690
even when you have a cough,

184
00:09:10,890 --> 00:09:12,730
your mother couldn't sleep all night.

185
00:09:12,820 --> 00:09:13,840
At midnight,

186
00:09:14,060 --> 00:09:14,930
no matter how late,

187
00:09:15,020 --> 00:09:16,050
she got up with a jerk.

188
00:09:16,140 --> 00:09:17,250
She had to see you

189
00:09:17,340 --> 00:09:18,220
how you are.

190
00:09:19,010 --> 00:09:20,210
She is your mother.

191
00:09:28,220 --> 00:09:29,290
Everyone says

192
00:09:30,060 --> 00:09:31,290
in this world

193
00:09:32,010 --> 00:09:33,640
the hardest thing

194
00:09:33,980 --> 00:09:35,400
is being a mother.

195
00:09:36,900 --> 00:09:38,450
If you hate someone extremely,

196
00:09:39,260 --> 00:09:40,800
you can tell God

197
00:09:41,370 --> 00:09:42,610
let this person

198
00:09:43,010 --> 00:09:43,970
in the next life

199
00:09:44,060 --> 00:09:45,200
be your mother.

200
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:48,180
So that you have a
lifetime to torment her.

201
00:10:31,090 --> 00:10:32,070
Li Qing Tong.

202
00:10:32,820 --> 00:10:34,710
Go home and apologize to your mother.

203
00:10:40,860 --> 00:10:41,990
Hua is sensible.

204
00:10:42,180 --> 00:10:43,720
Actually, I am not sensible.

205
00:10:44,060 --> 00:10:46,130
I was also doing whatever
I wanted to do before

206
00:10:46,220 --> 00:10:48,150
and didn't consider
other people's feelings.

207
00:10:48,490 --> 00:10:49,290
I always thought I was right

208
00:10:49,370 --> 00:10:50,570
and intelligent.

209
00:10:50,660 --> 00:10:52,720
In fact, I can do nothing
but lose my temper.

210
00:10:53,060 --> 00:10:54,600
After thinking like this,

211
00:10:54,970 --> 00:10:56,410
it's not easy for my mother

212
00:10:56,500 --> 00:10:58,200
to take care of me all by herself.

213
00:10:59,180 --> 00:11:00,170
In this world,

214
00:11:00,250 --> 00:11:01,840
every mother is not easy.

215
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:03,230
As the saying goes,

216
00:11:03,620 --> 00:11:04,810
if there are ten fathers,

217
00:11:04,900 --> 00:11:06,400
nine fathers fail,

218
00:11:06,660 --> 00:11:07,890
but if there are one hundred mothers,

219
00:11:07,980 --> 00:11:09,330
then ninety-nine mothers

220
00:11:09,420 --> 00:11:12,440
give all their attention
to their children.

221
00:11:13,770 --> 00:11:15,290
I don't need a father anyway.

222
00:11:15,380 --> 00:11:16,680
Me and my mother are enough.

223
00:11:18,500 --> 00:11:19,490
Hua, you silly child.

224
00:11:19,580 --> 00:11:20,490
I have just praised you.

225
00:11:20,580 --> 00:11:22,400
Why don't you need a father?

226
00:11:23,060 --> 00:11:26,160
I was the only one of the
ten fathers who qualified.

227
00:11:27,210 --> 00:11:27,390
Right.

228
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:28,210
Uncle, you are the best!

229
00:11:28,300 --> 00:11:29,180
Absolutely!

230
00:11:30,140 --> 00:11:30,690
Eat quickly.

231
00:11:30,780 --> 00:11:32,560
We will go back to apologize
to your mother after this meal.

232
00:11:43,540 --> 00:11:45,280
Just like what I told you.

233
00:11:46,420 --> 00:11:47,600
Go, go.

234
00:11:52,700 --> 00:11:54,330
Mum,

235
00:11:54,420 --> 00:11:56,090
I am sorry.

236
00:11:56,180 --> 00:11:57,800
I won't make you angry again.

237
00:11:57,890 --> 00:11:59,640
I'll do whatever you say.

238
00:12:01,420 --> 00:12:02,920
How about I sing you a song?

239
00:12:03,180 --> 00:12:03,930
The theme song of "Legend of Dagger Lee?"

240
00:12:04,020 --> 00:12:05,440
Your favourite.

241
00:12:06,490 --> 00:12:07,370
No.

242
00:12:07,780 --> 00:12:08,810
How about I help you do some housework?

243
00:12:08,900 --> 00:12:10,130
You tell me what work needs to be done.

244
00:12:10,220 --> 00:12:11,400
Didn't you do the dishes?

245
00:12:11,860 --> 00:12:13,080
Or I will help you to cook...

246
00:12:14,020 --> 00:12:16,000
It will be better if you don't
make me angry anymore.

247
00:12:16,340 --> 00:12:17,520
Doing housework?

248
00:12:19,570 --> 00:12:21,920
Please don't be mad.

249
00:12:22,180 --> 00:12:23,600
When you're angry,

250
00:12:25,290 --> 00:12:26,290
you make me so angry

251
00:12:26,380 --> 00:12:27,490
that my head hurts,

252
00:12:27,580 --> 00:12:28,610
my neck hurts,

253
00:12:28,700 --> 00:12:30,010
my stomach hurts.

254
00:12:30,100 --> 00:12:31,250
Every part of me hurts.

255
00:12:31,340 --> 00:12:33,430
I can't! I can't live anymore!

256
00:12:34,020 --> 00:12:36,040
Don't try to pull that
with me, I'm warning you.

257
00:12:38,340 --> 00:12:39,800
You guys haven't eaten yet, right?

258
00:12:42,980 --> 00:12:43,930
I'll make you some food.

259
00:12:44,010 --> 00:12:44,890
We have eaten

260
00:12:45,140 --> 00:12:45,930
in the restaurant

261
00:12:46,020 --> 00:12:47,050
and we also brought some food for you.

262
00:12:47,140 --> 00:12:48,240
What's that?

263
00:12:48,660 --> 00:12:49,540
Barbecue.

264
00:12:50,170 --> 00:12:51,240
Li Wu Si.

265
00:12:51,370 --> 00:12:52,970
Why did you take them to eat that stuff?

266
00:12:53,060 --> 00:12:55,400
It's so greasy and without nutrition.

267
00:12:55,660 --> 00:12:56,090
It's...

268
00:12:56,180 --> 00:12:57,000
It's because you didn't cook.

269
00:12:57,090 --> 00:12:59,170
I thought we couldn't let
the two kids be hungry,

270
00:12:59,260 --> 00:13:01,240
so I took them out to have a meal.

271
00:13:02,020 --> 00:13:02,920
Li Wu Si,

272
00:13:03,540 --> 00:13:04,420
come here.

273
00:13:04,940 --> 00:13:06,450
Should I be praised this time?

274
00:13:06,540 --> 00:13:07,840
Praising you?

275
00:13:09,260 --> 00:13:10,310
Where did the money for
the barbecue come from?

276
00:13:13,100 --> 00:13:14,000
On credit.

277
00:13:14,690 --> 00:13:16,230
I'm on credit with Liu. Ask
them if you don't believe me!

278
00:13:16,440 --> 00:13:17,320
On credit?

279
00:13:18,300 --> 00:13:18,690
Ok.

280
00:13:18,770 --> 00:13:19,650
I was really on credit!

281
00:13:19,740 --> 00:13:20,090
Aren't you great?

282
00:13:20,180 --> 00:13:21,170
No, no, you listen to me!

283
00:13:21,260 --> 00:13:21,770
You are lying!

284
00:13:21,850 --> 00:13:22,130
I'm not.

285
00:13:22,220 --> 00:13:22,930
How dare you hide private money!

286
00:13:23,020 --> 00:13:23,770
No, no, no.

287
00:13:23,860 --> 00:13:24,450
Li Wu Si.

288
00:13:24,540 --> 00:13:25,440
Don't, don't.

289
00:13:28,300 --> 00:13:30,840
Mum, he just drank!

290
00:13:40,890 --> 00:13:41,960
Li Qing Tong.

291
00:13:45,500 --> 00:13:47,590
Is it really hard to be a mother?

292
00:13:50,660 --> 00:13:53,360
I don't know. I haven't been a mother.

293
00:13:55,970 --> 00:13:56,850
Right.

294
00:13:57,100 --> 00:13:58,590
I've decided to forgive you.

295
00:14:00,130 --> 00:14:01,320
Hurry up, go to sleep.

296
00:14:12,180 --> 00:14:12,770
This time,

297
00:14:12,860 --> 00:14:14,230
The exam results are out.

298
00:14:14,500 --> 00:14:15,290
Here they are.

299
00:14:15,380 --> 00:14:17,920
First, I would like to
highlight two students.

300
00:14:18,380 --> 00:14:20,240
The first one is Li Jin Bu.

301
00:14:21,610 --> 00:14:22,680
As we all know,

302
00:14:23,100 --> 00:14:25,160
Li Jin Bu made some mistakes before,

303
00:14:25,330 --> 00:14:26,890
but they were all dealt with.

304
00:14:26,980 --> 00:14:29,130
With the human attitude, our school

305
00:14:29,220 --> 00:14:30,560
solved the matter.

306
00:14:30,820 --> 00:14:32,210
We hoped Li Jin Bu

307
00:14:32,300 --> 00:14:33,450
could learn from her mistakes

308
00:14:33,540 --> 00:14:34,910
and put her mind on her studies.

309
00:14:35,340 --> 00:14:36,400
I knew we were right.

310
00:14:37,010 --> 00:14:38,130
In our first big exam,

311
00:14:38,210 --> 00:14:39,130
Li Jin Bu

312
00:14:39,210 --> 00:14:40,950
ranked in the top 20 of our grade.

313
00:14:41,380 --> 00:14:42,970
She lived up to the
expectations of her teachers.

314
00:14:43,050 --> 00:14:44,810
I hope you all can learn from her

315
00:14:44,900 --> 00:14:45,730
to face the difficulties bravely.

316
00:14:45,810 --> 00:14:47,020
Let's applaud her!

317
00:14:52,290 --> 00:14:53,270
Next one,

318
00:14:53,610 --> 00:14:54,490
by coincidence,

319
00:14:54,660 --> 00:14:55,640
his surname is also Li,

320
00:14:55,980 --> 00:14:58,080
Let me keep you guessing.

321
00:14:58,380 --> 00:14:59,490
But I can tell you,

322
00:14:59,570 --> 00:15:00,490
this student's

323
00:15:00,580 --> 00:15:01,490
academic grades

324
00:15:01,580 --> 00:15:03,240
were always at the bottom of our class.

325
00:15:03,530 --> 00:15:04,480
But I have heard that

326
00:15:04,580 --> 00:15:06,830
recently he has been studying
late every day when he gets home.

327
00:15:06,930 --> 00:15:07,810
You see,

328
00:15:07,900 --> 00:15:10,000
the effect was immediately
visible on the paper.

329
00:15:10,570 --> 00:15:12,170
He ranked outside the top 100 before,

330
00:15:12,260 --> 00:15:14,070
but he ranked 65th this time.

331
00:15:14,660 --> 00:15:16,240
Such progress

332
00:15:16,460 --> 00:15:18,320
is more than any teacher
could have imagined.

333
00:15:18,490 --> 00:15:19,880
Do you know who I am talking about?

334
00:15:20,820 --> 00:15:22,450
Yes! That's Li Qiang!

335
00:15:22,540 --> 00:15:23,800
Let's applaud him!

336
00:15:30,860 --> 00:15:33,490
I hope you can be a
role model for everyone

337
00:15:33,570 --> 00:15:34,850
and make persistent efforts.

338
00:15:34,940 --> 00:15:36,570
Keep up the good work.
You can overcome anything.

339
00:15:36,650 --> 00:15:37,720
Never give up.

340
00:15:38,020 --> 00:15:38,920
Let's start our class.

341
00:15:39,360 --> 00:15:42,040
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

342
00:15:49,460 --> 00:15:50,950
Would you like to get something to eat?

343
00:16:00,540 --> 00:16:01,600
Then I'll go first.

344
00:16:08,620 --> 00:16:10,750
This is the result of my daily
supervision of your review.

345
00:16:12,460 --> 00:16:13,510
Sixty points for Chinese.

346
00:16:14,220 --> 00:16:15,050
Seventeen points for mathematics.

347
00:16:15,140 --> 00:16:16,880
Can you get lower grades?

348
00:16:17,130 --> 00:16:18,680
I have gotten lower grades previously.

349
00:16:18,770 --> 00:16:19,990
Am I praising you?

350
00:16:22,530 --> 00:16:24,880
Wu said you should not
always focus on grades.

351
00:16:25,100 --> 00:16:26,360
What should I focus on besides grades?

352
00:16:26,490 --> 00:16:27,450
Look at your grades,

353
00:16:27,540 --> 00:16:28,910
how do you get into college next year?

354
00:16:30,940 --> 00:16:32,870
Then I won't get into college.

355
00:16:33,020 --> 00:16:35,810
Not many people in this laggard
place would be able to go to college.

356
00:16:35,900 --> 00:16:38,440
Would you please stop being like this?

357
00:16:38,540 --> 00:16:40,410
Why can't you make a little effort now

358
00:16:40,500 --> 00:16:42,160
to reduce your burden for the future?

359
00:16:42,900 --> 00:16:44,080
I tried.

360
00:16:44,580 --> 00:16:46,730
Well, it takes talent to learn.

361
00:16:46,820 --> 00:16:48,920
I don't have talent. What can I do?

362
00:16:49,420 --> 00:16:50,840
You are not untalented at all.

363
00:16:51,450 --> 00:16:52,550
You are unpromising.

364
00:17:05,260 --> 00:17:07,630
How can my grades be so low?

365
00:17:09,339 --> 00:17:10,880
Did teachers make mistakes?

366
00:17:12,260 --> 00:17:14,569
[Daily Necessity Supermarket
and Restaurant]

367
00:17:15,980 --> 00:17:16,859
Okay.

368
00:17:26,380 --> 00:17:27,800
What's up?

369
00:17:30,260 --> 00:17:31,140
Shui Shui.

370
00:17:32,100 --> 00:17:34,880
I had a friend in Shenzhen
who was extremely like you.

371
00:17:35,180 --> 00:17:37,440
I always talk to her
when I am in a bad mood,

372
00:17:37,540 --> 00:17:39,840
so now I want to talk to you too.

373
00:17:41,620 --> 00:17:42,500
No problem.

374
00:17:42,660 --> 00:17:43,880
You've found the right person.

375
00:17:44,100 --> 00:17:44,690
Go ahead.

376
00:17:44,780 --> 00:17:46,240
Is it about Li Qing Tong?

377
00:17:46,340 --> 00:17:47,230
Yes.

378
00:17:47,780 --> 00:17:49,280
Thinking about Li Qing Tong,

379
00:17:49,740 --> 00:17:50,440
she is not good at studying

380
00:17:50,530 --> 00:17:51,630
and stupid.

381
00:17:52,530 --> 00:17:54,920
What if she becomes a loser in the future?

382
00:17:59,180 --> 00:18:00,120
Now that you mention it,

383
00:18:00,210 --> 00:18:01,550
I am also worried,

384
00:18:01,740 --> 00:18:03,750
but I am worried about myself.

385
00:18:03,940 --> 00:18:04,820
Seriously,

386
00:18:05,340 --> 00:18:06,770
talking about becoming a loser,

387
00:18:06,860 --> 00:18:08,680
we are both about the same.

388
00:18:09,180 --> 00:18:10,160
You don't need to worry.

389
00:18:10,300 --> 00:18:11,450
You'll be better than her in the future

390
00:18:11,540 --> 00:18:13,160
whether it's your
family life or your career.

391
00:18:13,460 --> 00:18:14,400
Really?

392
00:18:14,530 --> 00:18:17,000
For the first time in my life,
someone thinks I'm better than her.

393
00:18:18,340 --> 00:18:19,520
So,

394
00:18:19,980 --> 00:18:22,480
shall we just let Li Qing Tong
become a loser?

395
00:18:28,610 --> 00:18:31,320
Do you really want her to study hard?

396
00:18:31,690 --> 00:18:32,570
Certainly.

397
00:18:32,780 --> 00:18:34,090
Then I'll give you a

398
00:18:34,180 --> 00:18:36,680
master stroke.

399
00:18:37,940 --> 00:18:38,690
Right now,

400
00:18:38,780 --> 00:18:40,880
it's you who's pushing
her to study, right?

401
00:18:41,050 --> 00:18:41,930
Do you believe

402
00:18:42,020 --> 00:18:43,880
if you were replaced by someone else,

403
00:18:44,180 --> 00:18:45,490
no bother at all,

404
00:18:45,580 --> 00:18:46,970
just a look,

405
00:18:47,060 --> 00:18:49,800
Li Qing Tong will obediently go to study.

406
00:18:52,420 --> 00:18:53,090
Who to change?

407
00:18:53,180 --> 00:18:54,060
Wu Zhi Xun.

408
00:18:54,900 --> 00:18:56,040
Wu Zhi Xun?

409
00:18:57,980 --> 00:18:59,080
I'm not bragging.

410
00:18:59,380 --> 00:19:00,250
In the world,

411
00:19:00,340 --> 00:19:02,570
no one knows Li Qing Tong
better than I do.

412
00:19:02,660 --> 00:19:04,560
That's the power of an idol.

413
00:19:04,880 --> 00:19:07,320
Of course if you can get Leehom Wang,

414
00:19:07,570 --> 00:19:09,400
he can do the same.

415
00:19:12,290 --> 00:19:13,830
Then I'll ask Wu Zhi Xun.

416
00:19:15,180 --> 00:19:17,120
Then you might as well
ask Leehom Wang.

417
00:19:18,130 --> 00:19:19,110
What do you want to eat?

418
00:19:19,450 --> 00:19:20,000
Nothing.

419
00:19:20,090 --> 00:19:20,970
Canned food?

420
00:19:42,420 --> 00:19:43,300
What are you doing?

421
00:19:44,740 --> 00:19:45,800
Why don't you leave?

422
00:19:46,850 --> 00:19:48,040
You don't leave either.

423
00:19:49,020 --> 00:19:49,900
I...

424
00:19:50,100 --> 00:19:51,440
I forgot something.

425
00:20:04,450 --> 00:20:05,330
What's wrong?

426
00:20:05,740 --> 00:20:06,800
I want to have a word with you.

427
00:20:08,140 --> 00:20:09,020
Go ahead.

428
00:20:14,380 --> 00:20:16,360
You had trouble with Chen Jun He.

429
00:20:16,650 --> 00:20:18,480
By rights I should have done more

430
00:20:19,780 --> 00:20:20,760
but I'm a little unhappy.

431
00:20:22,810 --> 00:20:24,400
What does it matter to you?

432
00:20:24,780 --> 00:20:25,660
You are unhappy.

433
00:20:25,820 --> 00:20:26,960
Why are you unhappy?

434
00:20:28,700 --> 00:20:30,120
I really want to know

435
00:20:30,220 --> 00:20:32,270
what's the relationship
between you and Chen Jun He.

436
00:20:32,660 --> 00:20:34,290
Ever since you transferred to the school,

437
00:20:34,370 --> 00:20:35,440
the whole person has changed.

438
00:20:35,880 --> 00:20:37,110
You ignored us

439
00:20:37,660 --> 00:20:39,640
but paid all attention to Chen Jun He.

440
00:20:40,300 --> 00:20:41,840
You are such a nice little girl.

441
00:20:42,100 --> 00:20:44,270
Why are you always hanging
out with people like him?

442
00:20:44,490 --> 00:20:46,720
How do you make your classmates
and others think of you in the future?

443
00:20:48,180 --> 00:20:49,110
What about you?

444
00:20:49,940 --> 00:20:50,990
What do you think of me?

445
00:20:53,380 --> 00:20:54,600
You think

446
00:20:55,100 --> 00:20:56,490
I've just transferred to this school

447
00:20:56,580 --> 00:20:58,080
and I've already gotten into fights.

448
00:20:58,460 --> 00:21:00,840
The director took me to read
self-examination everywhere.

449
00:21:01,420 --> 00:21:03,310
I am a total troublemaker.

450
00:21:03,970 --> 00:21:05,070
Am I right?

451
00:21:05,460 --> 00:21:06,340
No.

452
00:21:06,820 --> 00:21:08,080
It doesn't matter if it is.

453
00:21:08,690 --> 00:21:10,160
That's just how I am.

454
00:21:10,540 --> 00:21:11,130
Rebel.

455
00:21:11,220 --> 00:21:11,890
Overbearing.

456
00:21:11,980 --> 00:21:12,860
Unreasonable.

457
00:21:13,380 --> 00:21:14,720
But that's how I am.

458
00:21:14,940 --> 00:21:16,440
I don't care what people think of me.

459
00:21:16,780 --> 00:21:18,760
Nobody wants to be my friend anyway.

460
00:21:20,500 --> 00:21:22,430
Who says no one wants to be your friend?

461
00:21:22,700 --> 00:21:24,110
I think you're nice.

462
00:21:25,780 --> 00:21:27,450
And don't look down on me.

463
00:21:27,540 --> 00:21:29,160
I'm not a regular person, either.

464
00:21:29,380 --> 00:21:31,320
I never care what people think of me.

465
00:21:31,420 --> 00:21:32,720
Birds of a feather flock together.

466
00:21:32,810 --> 00:21:34,040
It's good for us to be friends.

467
00:21:35,380 --> 00:21:36,600
Li Jin Bu.

468
00:21:42,220 --> 00:21:43,760
I didn't know Chen Jun He.

469
00:21:44,420 --> 00:21:46,670
I just made a mistake
with him by accident.

470
00:21:47,060 --> 00:21:49,880
I just don't like people like him
who are so smug and unreasonable.

471
00:21:49,970 --> 00:21:51,360
That's why I wanted to teach him a lesson.

472
00:21:52,420 --> 00:21:53,410
That's what it is.

473
00:21:53,490 --> 00:21:54,590
Believe it or not.

474
00:21:54,780 --> 00:21:55,330
I believe.

475
00:21:55,420 --> 00:21:56,350
Li Jin Bu.

476
00:21:56,860 --> 00:21:57,770
Wait for me, Li Jin Bu!

477
00:21:57,860 --> 00:21:58,490
Let's go together.

478
00:21:58,580 --> 00:21:59,460
I believe.

479
00:22:04,620 --> 00:22:05,680
Hua.

480
00:22:06,690 --> 00:22:08,550
Are you still angry?

481
00:22:10,330 --> 00:22:13,000
I promise I won't get
such low grades again.

482
00:22:15,700 --> 00:22:17,590
These are all Wu Zhi Xun's papers.

483
00:22:19,260 --> 00:22:20,920
He's very terrific.

484
00:22:21,620 --> 00:22:22,450
Look.

485
00:22:22,530 --> 00:22:23,680
A liberal arts student.

486
00:22:23,820 --> 00:22:25,650
Full marks in half of the math tests.

487
00:22:25,730 --> 00:22:27,490
Not to mention history,
geography, politics and English.

488
00:22:27,580 --> 00:22:29,160
Only Chinese is a little bit worse.

489
00:22:30,010 --> 00:22:32,850
He must always rank first in your class.

490
00:22:32,940 --> 00:22:35,560
He even always ranks first in our grade.

491
00:22:37,540 --> 00:22:39,440
One time, he made a
mistake on a math problem

492
00:22:39,740 --> 00:22:41,480
and he was so angry
that he tore up the papers.

493
00:22:46,900 --> 00:22:47,730
But

494
00:22:47,820 --> 00:22:49,920
where did you get his papers?

495
00:22:50,180 --> 00:22:51,330
There are so many in his desk drawer.

496
00:22:51,420 --> 00:22:52,790
I took some back furtively.

497
00:22:53,220 --> 00:22:54,720
Why did you take his papers?

498
00:22:56,650 --> 00:22:58,040
Do you especially admire him?

499
00:22:59,820 --> 00:23:00,700
Of course.

500
00:23:01,420 --> 00:23:02,400
Look at him,

501
00:23:02,740 --> 00:23:03,790
not only can get good grades

502
00:23:03,880 --> 00:23:04,680
but also be handsome.

503
00:23:04,770 --> 00:23:05,990
Then,

504
00:23:06,180 --> 00:23:07,890
if Wu Zhi Xun wants to
help you with your studies,

505
00:23:07,970 --> 00:23:08,850
will you accept it?

506
00:23:11,900 --> 00:23:14,030
Wu Zhi Xun help me with my studies?

507
00:23:15,660 --> 00:23:18,160
Why don't you let Yang Ai Ling
take me to play truant?

508
00:23:49,820 --> 00:23:50,800
Excuse me,

509
00:23:51,460 --> 00:23:53,090
can I discuss something with you?

510
00:23:53,180 --> 00:23:54,060
No.

511
00:23:55,460 --> 00:23:56,560
Just two minutes.

512
00:23:56,810 --> 00:23:57,690
No.

513
00:24:07,340 --> 00:24:08,220
Hi,

514
00:24:08,480 --> 00:24:08,850
you,

515
00:24:08,930 --> 00:24:10,830
you can listen to me when you walk.

516
00:24:11,180 --> 00:24:12,440
What do you want to say on earth?

517
00:24:12,620 --> 00:24:14,840
Well, there's something
I'd like to discuss with you.

518
00:24:15,380 --> 00:24:16,260
Hua.

519
00:24:16,700 --> 00:24:17,680
Save me!

520
00:24:17,940 --> 00:24:18,690
Don't hit me!

521
00:24:18,780 --> 00:24:19,660
You come.

522
00:24:20,660 --> 00:24:21,680
You come first.

523
00:24:22,450 --> 00:24:23,210
What's up?

524
00:24:23,300 --> 00:24:23,570
Don't,

525
00:24:23,660 --> 00:24:24,490
don't hit me.

526
00:24:24,580 --> 00:24:25,440
Ba Dan.

527
00:24:25,530 --> 00:24:26,730
You are something else!

528
00:24:26,820 --> 00:24:28,510
I thought highly of you.

529
00:24:28,850 --> 00:24:30,560
You get a girl to save you.

530
00:24:30,660 --> 00:24:32,030
Is she an average girl?

531
00:24:32,220 --> 00:24:33,400
She is Hua!

532
00:24:33,620 --> 00:24:35,450
She kicked Chen Jun He
down a few days ago.

533
00:24:35,540 --> 00:24:36,330
Have you heard that?

534
00:24:36,420 --> 00:24:37,400
She has learned kung fu.

535
00:24:37,850 --> 00:24:38,570
Are you afraid?

536
00:24:38,660 --> 00:24:40,270
Seriously?

537
00:24:40,420 --> 00:24:41,800
Where did you learn kung fu?

538
00:24:43,900 --> 00:24:45,010
It's none of your business.

539
00:24:45,100 --> 00:24:46,000
What are you doing?

540
00:24:46,260 --> 00:24:48,600
He broke my brother's roller skates

541
00:24:48,820 --> 00:24:50,600
and kicked my brother in the ditch.

542
00:24:50,780 --> 00:24:52,010
He was too arrogant.

543
00:24:52,100 --> 00:24:52,980
Don't be so shameless.

544
00:24:53,300 --> 00:24:54,180
Stand there.

545
00:24:54,340 --> 00:24:55,400
Hua, right?

546
00:24:55,780 --> 00:24:57,640
I don't care who you are.

547
00:24:57,980 --> 00:24:59,810
Even if the school bully comes,

548
00:24:59,900 --> 00:25:01,250
he needs to be reasonable.

549
00:25:01,340 --> 00:25:02,800
I really didn't break those.

550
00:25:03,050 --> 00:25:04,030
His roller skates have been broken before.

551
00:25:04,120 --> 00:25:05,240
He wanted to rob my shoes

552
00:25:05,340 --> 00:25:06,680
so we fought

553
00:25:06,940 --> 00:25:08,350
and he slid into the ditch by himself.

554
00:25:08,940 --> 00:25:09,850
Listen to him,

555
00:25:09,940 --> 00:25:10,690
who is unreasonable?

556
00:25:10,770 --> 00:25:12,040
He is talking nonsense!

557
00:25:12,500 --> 00:25:13,490
If he doesn't compensate today,

558
00:25:13,580 --> 00:25:14,560
I will hit him.

559
00:25:14,730 --> 00:25:15,250
Calm down.

560
00:25:15,340 --> 00:25:16,210
Let him go.

561
00:25:16,300 --> 00:25:16,770
Let him go.

562
00:25:16,860 --> 00:25:17,530
You guys don't hit him!

563
00:25:17,620 --> 00:25:18,770
Hua and Chen Jun He are buddies.

564
00:25:18,860 --> 00:25:19,880
You think about it.

565
00:25:20,580 --> 00:25:21,460
Who's there?

566
00:25:24,170 --> 00:25:26,000
What school do you come from?

567
00:25:26,260 --> 00:25:27,200
Do you know who I am?

568
00:25:27,900 --> 00:25:28,610
Chen.

569
00:25:28,690 --> 00:25:29,790
We come from the No.1 Middle School.

570
00:25:29,880 --> 00:25:31,070
We came here to get some justice.

571
00:25:31,500 --> 00:25:32,430
What justice?

572
00:25:32,620 --> 00:25:34,480
He broke my brother's roller skates.

573
00:25:34,620 --> 00:25:35,750
Do you think he has to pay for these?

574
00:25:36,020 --> 00:25:36,690
These,

575
00:25:36,780 --> 00:25:38,130
these were not broken by me!

576
00:25:38,220 --> 00:25:40,250
It was his brother who broke his
own roller skates and took mine.

577
00:25:40,340 --> 00:25:41,930
A lot of students from No.1 and No.3
Middle Schools were there at that time.

578
00:25:42,010 --> 00:25:43,480
If you don't believe
me, let's ask someone.

579
00:25:44,180 --> 00:25:44,970
Bro,

580
00:25:45,060 --> 00:25:46,690
you came to our school for justice,

581
00:25:46,780 --> 00:25:48,090
then you should obey our rules.

582
00:25:48,170 --> 00:25:49,060
Go back and get your brother here

583
00:25:49,150 --> 00:25:50,910
and let's find some students
who were there at that time.

584
00:25:51,120 --> 00:25:53,210
If everyone says he broke the shoes,

585
00:25:53,300 --> 00:25:53,890
even if he doesn't pay,

586
00:25:53,980 --> 00:25:54,990
I will pay for you.

587
00:25:55,260 --> 00:25:56,310
But if not,

588
00:25:56,970 --> 00:25:57,770
bro,

589
00:25:57,850 --> 00:26:00,080
we need to search for justice,

590
00:26:00,220 --> 00:26:01,090
okay?

591
00:26:01,180 --> 00:26:01,600
Let it pass.

592
00:26:01,690 --> 00:26:02,610
Show Chen some courtesy.

593
00:26:02,690 --> 00:26:03,690
We are unlucky today.

594
00:26:03,780 --> 00:26:04,410
Ba Dan.

595
00:26:04,500 --> 00:26:05,250
You remember that

596
00:26:05,330 --> 00:26:07,120
don't let me see you at the rink.

597
00:26:07,530 --> 00:26:08,410
Let's go.

598
00:26:10,460 --> 00:26:11,890
No one wants to go there.

599
00:26:11,980 --> 00:26:13,000
The environment there is poor.

600
00:26:13,220 --> 00:26:14,440
Shut up.

601
00:26:17,300 --> 00:26:18,990
I have a lot of homework today.

602
00:26:20,180 --> 00:26:21,060
Wang Xiao Min.

603
00:26:21,340 --> 00:26:22,610
You are afraid of trouble
but make trouble all day

604
00:26:22,700 --> 00:26:24,240
and then you say out my name.

605
00:26:24,660 --> 00:26:25,910
Who gave you the courage?

606
00:26:26,100 --> 00:26:27,400
Do you want a beating?

607
00:26:28,980 --> 00:26:30,120
I am sorry. I am sorry.

608
00:26:30,460 --> 00:26:32,630
Give me a break for my sister's sake.

609
00:26:32,730 --> 00:26:33,800
Who is your sister?

610
00:26:34,100 --> 00:26:35,150
Li Qing Tong.

611
00:26:35,250 --> 00:26:37,200
You guys are on good terms right now.

612
00:26:37,300 --> 00:26:38,960
I saw you buy her a bag.

613
00:26:39,260 --> 00:26:39,850
I have heard that

614
00:26:39,940 --> 00:26:41,370
a few days ago her words

615
00:26:41,460 --> 00:26:42,290
touched you

616
00:26:42,380 --> 00:26:43,510
and made you cry.

617
00:26:45,700 --> 00:26:46,960
Who told you that?

618
00:26:47,740 --> 00:26:48,790
Herself.

619
00:26:49,450 --> 00:26:50,520
Don't be ridiculous!

620
00:26:51,420 --> 00:26:52,250
Made me cry?

621
00:26:52,330 --> 00:26:53,450
I'll make you cry in a minute.

622
00:26:53,530 --> 00:26:54,410
Do you believe it?

623
00:26:54,820 --> 00:26:56,010
Yes, yes.

624
00:26:56,100 --> 00:26:56,770
I believe.

625
00:26:56,860 --> 00:26:57,760
Today I'll let you go.

626
00:26:58,250 --> 00:26:59,650
Go back and tell Li Qing Tong

627
00:26:59,740 --> 00:27:01,160
not to bad-mouth me.

628
00:27:01,420 --> 00:27:03,400
If I hear it one more time, man,

629
00:27:03,700 --> 00:27:04,870
I'll hit you first.

630
00:27:10,690 --> 00:27:11,710
Wait, bro.

631
00:27:11,840 --> 00:27:12,710
She's the one bad-mouthing you.

632
00:27:12,790 --> 00:27:14,420
Why are you hitting me?

633
00:27:41,610 --> 00:27:43,080
Do you have time now?

634
00:27:44,540 --> 00:27:45,880
Can you change up your words?

635
00:27:46,330 --> 00:27:47,210
Look,

636
00:27:47,420 --> 00:27:48,490
you won't talk to me.

637
00:27:48,580 --> 00:27:49,920
What can I do?

638
00:27:50,500 --> 00:27:51,890
At least we are deskmates.

639
00:27:51,980 --> 00:27:53,520
You wouldn't be so cold.

640
00:27:53,740 --> 00:27:54,620
Excuse me,

641
00:27:54,860 --> 00:27:56,640
we can not be deskmates either.

642
00:27:56,940 --> 00:27:58,650
I suggest you change your seat.

643
00:27:58,740 --> 00:28:01,480
I really don't have
time for people like you.

644
00:28:02,170 --> 00:28:03,330
What do you mean people like me?

645
00:28:03,420 --> 00:28:04,440
What kind of people?

646
00:28:05,020 --> 00:28:06,720
A person who makes trouble every day.

647
00:28:11,580 --> 00:28:12,480
Wu Zhi Xun.

648
00:28:13,260 --> 00:28:15,040
Where are you going in self-study courses?

649
00:28:19,060 --> 00:28:20,790
Something wrong with his head?

650
00:28:23,980 --> 00:28:26,760
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

651
00:28:29,620 --> 00:28:31,880
It's the first time I've seen
someone who speaks so badly.

652
00:28:32,420 --> 00:28:33,570
He talked to you!

653
00:28:33,650 --> 00:28:34,490
What's wrong?

654
00:28:34,580 --> 00:28:35,920
He's not dumb.

655
00:28:38,700 --> 00:28:40,470
We have both been
classmates for two years.

656
00:28:40,980 --> 00:28:42,990
He said two sentences to me altogether.

657
00:28:43,890 --> 00:28:44,840
What's that?

658
00:28:46,530 --> 00:28:47,410
Classmate,

659
00:28:47,620 --> 00:28:48,760
excuse me.

660
00:28:49,820 --> 00:28:51,150
Isn't it just one sentence?

661
00:28:51,420 --> 00:28:52,300
Twice.

662
00:28:53,820 --> 00:28:56,250
I thought he was dumb in the
whole first year of high school,

663
00:28:56,330 --> 00:28:58,200
if he didn't answer questions in class.

664
00:28:58,290 --> 00:28:59,390
I was shocked at that time.

665
00:29:00,220 --> 00:29:02,650
You guys don't laugh at him here.

666
00:29:02,740 --> 00:29:04,280
I think he is nice.

667
00:29:04,620 --> 00:29:06,450
He was so devoted and

668
00:29:06,540 --> 00:29:07,600
preoccupied

669
00:29:07,740 --> 00:29:09,120
with his studies.

670
00:29:09,680 --> 00:29:10,800
You don't understand.

671
00:29:11,340 --> 00:29:13,690
Only you and Lin Xue Wei
in our class think he is nice.

672
00:29:13,780 --> 00:29:15,330
No one else cares for him.

673
00:29:15,420 --> 00:29:18,110
What does Lin Xue Wei know?

674
00:29:18,300 --> 00:29:19,650
She has no substance

675
00:29:19,740 --> 00:29:20,490
and only focuses on appearance.

676
00:29:20,580 --> 00:29:21,600
Superficial.

677
00:29:36,480 --> 00:29:38,960
[Be quiet inside the room]

678
00:29:40,770 --> 00:29:42,400
So handsome.

679
00:29:44,060 --> 00:29:45,240
Go back to studying!

680
00:29:54,620 --> 00:29:57,360
Happy holiday!

681
00:29:58,460 --> 00:29:59,250
Pick it up.

682
00:29:59,340 --> 00:30:00,760
You have to wash it by
yourself after going home.

683
00:30:07,020 --> 00:30:08,800
Why are you all so sad?

684
00:30:09,220 --> 00:30:10,100
Don't ask me.

685
00:30:10,740 --> 00:30:12,790
I have mixed feelings now.

686
00:30:13,100 --> 00:30:14,560
After all, I got a free tutor

687
00:30:14,650 --> 00:30:16,280
staring at me at home every day.

688
00:30:21,300 --> 00:30:21,970
Don't panic.

689
00:30:22,060 --> 00:30:23,610
Li Qing Tong is not the last one.

690
00:30:23,690 --> 00:30:24,930
What do you have to worry about?

691
00:30:25,010 --> 00:30:26,880
Ba Dan got lower grades than Li Qing Tong.

692
00:30:26,970 --> 00:30:28,280
He doesn't even worry.

693
00:30:28,410 --> 00:30:30,240
Happy holiday!

694
00:30:32,540 --> 00:30:33,440
Look.

695
00:30:34,300 --> 00:30:37,000
How can I get lower grades than him?

696
00:30:37,090 --> 00:30:38,400
Then I'm going to die.

697
00:30:41,460 --> 00:30:42,710
Ba Dan, your bag!

698
00:30:43,140 --> 00:30:44,120
Ba Dan!

699
00:30:50,900 --> 00:30:51,840
Where's my uncle?

700
00:30:52,140 --> 00:30:53,530
I haven't seen him all day.

701
00:30:53,610 --> 00:30:55,120
I think he went to the school.

702
00:30:55,690 --> 00:30:56,570
The school?

703
00:30:57,250 --> 00:30:58,550
Why did he go to the school on a holiday?

704
00:30:58,940 --> 00:31:00,310
Yang Ai Ling asked for it.

705
00:31:02,380 --> 00:31:03,630
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

706
00:31:07,570 --> 00:31:10,360
Have you done something bad recently?

707
00:31:10,890 --> 00:31:12,310
What bad things can I do?

708
00:31:13,580 --> 00:31:15,680
I have heard from Niu Xiao Huo that

709
00:31:15,980 --> 00:31:18,090
you gave a bag to a girl

710
00:31:18,180 --> 00:31:19,880
and cottoned up to her.

711
00:31:22,060 --> 00:31:23,280
Niu Xiao Huo told you, right?

712
00:31:23,970 --> 00:31:24,730
Fine.

713
00:31:24,820 --> 00:31:26,120
See if I don't kill him tomorrow.

714
00:31:26,490 --> 00:31:28,030
Take a break.

715
00:31:28,700 --> 00:31:31,280
Just wait till your uncle comes back.

716
00:31:32,500 --> 00:31:33,410
You this jerk.

717
00:31:33,500 --> 00:31:35,410
You always don't know
it when you're well off.

718
00:31:35,500 --> 00:31:38,090
If my family were willing
to pay for my education,

719
00:31:38,170 --> 00:31:40,080
do I need to wash the pond here every day?

720
00:31:41,570 --> 00:31:42,640
Or you can change with me.

721
00:31:42,740 --> 00:31:43,410
You go to school

722
00:31:43,500 --> 00:31:44,640
and I wash the pond here.

723
00:31:46,060 --> 00:31:47,630
Let's change.

724
00:31:48,700 --> 00:31:49,760
Uncle, you are back.

725
00:31:49,900 --> 00:31:51,250
You work here from now on

726
00:31:51,340 --> 00:31:52,890
and I go to school to make trouble.

727
00:31:52,980 --> 00:31:53,850
Boss, I have something to report to you.

728
00:31:53,940 --> 00:31:55,840
You stand aside. I am
dealing with my family matters.

729
00:31:56,620 --> 00:31:57,970
Uncle, business is important.

730
00:31:58,060 --> 00:31:58,640
You work first.

731
00:31:58,730 --> 00:31:59,330
Business first.

732
00:31:59,410 --> 00:32:00,880
Did you know business is important?

733
00:32:01,170 --> 00:32:02,050
You have

734
00:32:02,300 --> 00:32:03,690
disgraced me.

735
00:32:03,780 --> 00:32:05,160
It doesn't matter if you can't study well.

736
00:32:07,330 --> 00:32:08,370
You went to another class

737
00:32:08,460 --> 00:32:10,100
to make trouble with a
girl from a lower grade.

738
00:32:10,180 --> 00:32:11,210
I didn't make trouble with the girl.

739
00:32:11,290 --> 00:32:12,510
Don't listen to them.

740
00:32:12,700 --> 00:32:13,710
Okay, fine.

741
00:32:16,130 --> 00:32:17,040
Sure, laugh.

742
00:32:20,740 --> 00:32:22,000
You are still laughing?

743
00:32:22,340 --> 00:32:24,170
I worked so hard to raise you.

744
00:32:24,260 --> 00:32:25,650
That's how you repay me,

745
00:32:25,740 --> 00:32:26,450
right?

746
00:32:26,540 --> 00:32:29,450
If I don't beat you,
how can I face your parents?

747
00:32:29,540 --> 00:32:31,560
Look at this.

748
00:32:31,700 --> 00:32:32,530
Boss.

749
00:32:32,620 --> 00:32:34,480
You get out of my way.

750
00:32:35,460 --> 00:32:36,290
Don't be so angry.

751
00:32:36,370 --> 00:32:37,520
Don't beat him!

752
00:32:45,610 --> 00:32:48,280
Just give me another minute.

753
00:32:49,130 --> 00:32:49,850
Nope.

754
00:32:49,940 --> 00:32:50,530
Don't be lazy.

755
00:32:50,620 --> 00:32:52,040
You have rested for more than ten minutes.

756
00:32:52,620 --> 00:32:55,450
But who does their homework
at the very beginning of holidays?

757
00:32:55,530 --> 00:32:57,360
It's too stifling.

758
00:32:58,580 --> 00:32:59,160
Get up.

759
00:32:59,250 --> 00:33:00,150
Get up. Get up.

760
00:33:00,370 --> 00:33:01,450
You think I want to supervise you?

761
00:33:01,540 --> 00:33:03,450
If I had a better way I'd leave you alone.

762
00:33:03,540 --> 00:33:04,520
Do your homework.

763
00:33:05,500 --> 00:33:06,880
I can't.

764
00:33:07,260 --> 00:33:08,160
Li Qing Tong.

765
00:33:08,420 --> 00:33:08,930
You get up quickly!

766
00:33:09,020 --> 00:33:10,680
I tell you don't be shameless.

767
00:33:11,400 --> 00:33:13,530
Why are you here?

768
00:33:13,620 --> 00:33:14,210
Hua.

769
00:33:14,300 --> 00:33:15,970
You come out to eat if you are hungry.

770
00:33:16,060 --> 00:33:18,040
She can't eat until she
finishes her homework.

771
00:33:19,020 --> 00:33:20,320
Kids should eat on time.

772
00:33:20,420 --> 00:33:21,360
Right.

773
00:33:23,980 --> 00:33:25,200
Other times are fine.

774
00:33:28,220 --> 00:33:29,480
Do you want this if you are hungry?

775
00:33:39,380 --> 00:33:40,200
It's no use staring at me.

776
00:33:40,290 --> 00:33:41,130
Do your homework.

777
00:33:41,220 --> 00:33:42,480
I can't.

778
00:33:43,260 --> 00:33:44,150
I'll teach you.

779
00:33:46,740 --> 00:33:47,850
I don't want to listen.

780
00:33:47,940 --> 00:33:48,560
I can't understand you.

781
00:33:48,650 --> 00:33:50,250
I can't understand anything.

782
00:33:50,340 --> 00:33:51,950
Here, look at this question.

783
00:33:54,810 --> 00:33:55,770
I've already cooked.

784
00:33:55,860 --> 00:33:56,690
It's in the kitchen.

785
00:33:56,780 --> 00:33:57,660
Ok.

786
00:33:58,010 --> 00:33:58,890
Take care.

787
00:33:59,650 --> 00:34:00,000
Auntie.

788
00:34:00,090 --> 00:34:00,810
What are you doing here?

789
00:34:00,900 --> 00:34:01,530
I came to see my sister.

790
00:34:01,620 --> 00:34:02,640
Don't see your sister.

791
00:34:02,730 --> 00:34:03,210
She is busy.

792
00:34:03,290 --> 00:34:03,850
Go play outside.

793
00:34:03,940 --> 00:34:04,210
No, no, no.

794
00:34:04,290 --> 00:34:04,730
I...

795
00:34:04,820 --> 00:34:05,720
I came to see my uncle.

796
00:34:05,810 --> 00:34:07,200
Came to see your uncle?

797
00:34:07,460 --> 00:34:08,489
I missed my uncle.

798
00:34:08,570 --> 00:34:09,530
I want to talk with my uncle.

799
00:34:09,620 --> 00:34:10,290
Uncle.

800
00:34:10,380 --> 00:34:12,010
Why don't you let him in?

801
00:34:12,090 --> 00:34:12,610
Du, come in.

802
00:34:12,699 --> 00:34:13,580
Okay.

803
00:34:14,290 --> 00:34:14,810
Did you have a meal?

804
00:34:14,900 --> 00:34:15,370
I did.

805
00:34:15,460 --> 00:34:16,340
Come back.

806
00:34:17,139 --> 00:34:18,290
Your sister is studying in that room.

807
00:34:18,370 --> 00:34:19,880
Don't bother her!

808
00:34:19,980 --> 00:34:20,570
I say,

809
00:34:20,659 --> 00:34:21,969
Auntie, don't tell jokes.

810
00:34:22,060 --> 00:34:23,370
Can my sister study?

811
00:34:23,460 --> 00:34:25,480
If she can study, I will eat
the washing machine.

812
00:34:25,659 --> 00:34:26,730
Then you eat the washing machine.

813
00:34:26,820 --> 00:34:28,560
Or he'll break it.

814
00:34:29,050 --> 00:34:30,090
I have to go now.

815
00:34:30,179 --> 00:34:31,290
Keep an eye on him.

816
00:34:31,380 --> 00:34:32,090
If he goes to that room,

817
00:34:32,179 --> 00:34:32,969
I'll be angry with you two.

818
00:34:33,060 --> 00:34:33,650
Just go.

819
00:34:33,739 --> 00:34:35,010
You're always angry.

820
00:34:35,090 --> 00:34:36,400
I will be angry with you first after
I'm back.

821
00:34:39,610 --> 00:34:40,710
Is she really studying?

822
00:34:41,409 --> 00:34:42,350
Really.

823
00:34:44,770 --> 00:34:47,360
What does my sister
look like while studying?

824
00:34:47,969 --> 00:34:48,929
I'll have a look.

825
00:34:49,020 --> 00:34:49,920
Wait a minute!

826
00:34:58,300 --> 00:34:59,180
Go.

827
00:35:20,210 --> 00:35:22,280
I said I shouldn't expect anything.

828
00:35:22,580 --> 00:35:24,320
It's a familiar scene.

829
00:35:25,780 --> 00:35:27,160
Too familiar.

830
00:35:34,460 --> 00:35:35,340
I say...

831
00:35:36,490 --> 00:35:38,280
Why did you sleep too?

832
00:35:38,740 --> 00:35:40,550
I was influenced by you.

833
00:35:42,060 --> 00:35:44,310
What a waste of time
sleeping in the daytime.

834
00:35:47,810 --> 00:35:49,080
Let's go play with dogs.

835
00:35:49,300 --> 00:35:50,730
There are several big
dogs in my classmate's house.

836
00:35:50,820 --> 00:35:51,770
So big.

837
00:35:51,860 --> 00:35:52,730
Shall we go?

838
00:35:52,820 --> 00:35:54,030
Ok, ok, ok.

839
00:35:54,850 --> 00:35:55,730
No.

840
00:35:56,290 --> 00:35:58,440
She can't go anywhere until
she finishes these papers.

841
00:35:59,780 --> 00:36:02,000
It's the holidays.
Why are you so strict?

842
00:36:02,620 --> 00:36:03,330
Listen to him.

843
00:36:03,420 --> 00:36:05,010
Listen to others' opinions.

844
00:36:05,090 --> 00:36:07,000
Others can't stand it.

845
00:36:08,730 --> 00:36:09,650
Your mother has gone out.

846
00:36:09,740 --> 00:36:10,370
Come, come.

847
00:36:10,460 --> 00:36:11,330
Come to eat.

848
00:36:11,420 --> 00:36:11,730
Yeah!

849
00:36:11,810 --> 00:36:12,330
Uncle,

850
00:36:12,420 --> 00:36:13,720
I have eaten.

851
00:36:25,100 --> 00:36:26,110
Du...

852
00:36:26,580 --> 00:36:28,250
Slow down. Haven't you eaten?

853
00:36:28,340 --> 00:36:28,610
It doesn't matter.

854
00:36:28,700 --> 00:36:29,710
I can still eat.

855
00:36:29,800 --> 00:36:30,760
Don't waste food.

856
00:36:31,020 --> 00:36:32,390
Sweetie, here, eat one.

857
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:33,160
Hua.

858
00:36:33,250 --> 00:36:34,470
Eat one quickly.

859
00:36:34,900 --> 00:36:36,320
Otherwise Du will eat them up.

860
00:36:37,990 --> 00:36:38,870
Dad.

861
00:36:40,180 --> 00:36:41,880
Can I go out later?

862
00:36:43,100 --> 00:36:43,980
What are you going to do?

863
00:36:46,690 --> 00:36:48,200
Studying in the library.

864
00:36:50,940 --> 00:36:51,960
Li Qing Tong,

865
00:36:52,180 --> 00:36:53,520
how hard the chairs are in the library,

866
00:36:53,610 --> 00:36:55,270
you should sleep somewhere else.

867
00:36:55,480 --> 00:36:56,840
Don't eat!

868
00:37:02,090 --> 00:37:04,240
I... I'm just going out for a second.

869
00:37:05,260 --> 00:37:06,010
I promise

870
00:37:06,100 --> 00:37:07,490
before my mum gets back,

871
00:37:07,580 --> 00:37:08,730
I'll be at home.

872
00:37:08,810 --> 00:37:11,110
I won't let her know you let me out.

873
00:37:11,380 --> 00:37:12,000
No.

874
00:37:12,090 --> 00:37:13,280
Your mother doesn't let you out

875
00:37:13,650 --> 00:37:15,130
and she will be angry
with me if you go out.

876
00:37:15,220 --> 00:37:16,330
Last time she was angry with me,

877
00:37:16,420 --> 00:37:18,030
but I didn't see you
say a few words for me.

878
00:37:20,130 --> 00:37:21,480
Li Wu Si.

879
00:37:22,260 --> 00:37:23,400
I promise you

880
00:37:23,740 --> 00:37:24,890
if she does find out this time,

881
00:37:24,970 --> 00:37:26,010
I'm absolutely on my own.

882
00:37:26,100 --> 00:37:27,440
I'm not a drag on you at all.

883
00:37:29,780 --> 00:37:30,450
No.

884
00:37:30,540 --> 00:37:31,420
I don't believe you.

885
00:37:38,660 --> 00:37:39,250
If you don't let me out,

886
00:37:39,340 --> 00:37:40,960
I'll tell my mum you drink at home.

887
00:37:49,060 --> 00:37:49,950
I don't drink.

888
00:37:55,980 --> 00:37:56,860
I don't eat.

889
00:38:01,820 --> 00:38:02,700
Why don't you do that?

890
00:38:03,460 --> 00:38:05,350
Your mum asked Hua to supervise you.

891
00:38:05,860 --> 00:38:07,050
Then you can ask Hua.

892
00:38:07,140 --> 00:38:07,810
If she agrees,

893
00:38:07,890 --> 00:38:08,920
I will agree.

894
00:38:15,840 --> 00:38:16,720
No way.

895
00:38:19,940 --> 00:38:21,400
Heartless.

896
00:38:21,780 --> 00:38:22,680
I won't eat.

897
00:38:24,930 --> 00:38:26,270
Look at yourself.

898
00:38:30,820 --> 00:38:32,600
It's terrible not to be good at school.

899
00:38:34,730 --> 00:38:35,330
Hua.

900
00:38:35,420 --> 00:38:36,910
Why don't you and I go out and play?

901
00:38:37,000 --> 00:38:37,880
Just eat.

902
00:38:43,850 --> 00:38:44,390
Li Qing Tong .

903
00:38:44,480 --> 00:38:45,360
Go out.

904
00:38:47,370 --> 00:38:48,570
I'm not saying I won't study.

905
00:38:48,660 --> 00:38:49,610
But you aren't studying.

906
00:38:49,690 --> 00:38:50,770
It's the winter holiday.

907
00:38:50,860 --> 00:38:52,090
You only got more than
ten points in the exam.

908
00:38:52,180 --> 00:38:53,650
Do you deserve the winter holiday?

909
00:38:53,740 --> 00:38:54,650
Keep your voice down.

910
00:38:54,740 --> 00:38:56,290
They don't know about it.

911
00:38:56,380 --> 00:38:57,520
Since you're going out anyway,

912
00:38:57,610 --> 00:38:59,560
I will tell your parents
you changed the score.

913
00:38:59,930 --> 00:39:00,890
What's wrong with you?

914
00:39:00,980 --> 00:39:02,050
Are we still friends?

915
00:39:02,130 --> 00:39:03,810
If you keep doing this, I'll die young.

916
00:39:03,890 --> 00:39:05,800
I can not be your friend
if it makes you better.

917
00:39:08,220 --> 00:39:08,850
Li Qing Tong,

918
00:39:08,940 --> 00:39:10,650
I know I'm being a bore now.

919
00:39:10,740 --> 00:39:11,890
I also want to spend the winter holiday

920
00:39:11,980 --> 00:39:12,770
playing with you.

921
00:39:12,860 --> 00:39:15,320
But we have to think
about the future, don't we?

922
00:39:17,580 --> 00:39:18,950
I know you have my best interests
at heart,

923
00:39:19,610 --> 00:39:20,890
but this is not the first time

924
00:39:20,980 --> 00:39:23,080
I failed the exams.

925
00:39:23,250 --> 00:39:25,290
We can't affect our
relationship for many years

926
00:39:25,380 --> 00:39:26,770
due to this little thing.

927
00:39:26,860 --> 00:39:27,750
Do you think so?

928
00:39:27,940 --> 00:39:28,690
First of all,

929
00:39:28,780 --> 00:39:30,120
study is not a little thing.

930
00:39:30,610 --> 00:39:31,490
Next,

931
00:39:31,730 --> 00:39:33,330
if this thing can affect our relationship,

932
00:39:33,420 --> 00:39:35,840
it will prove that we haven't been
in a real relationship for years.

933
00:39:37,670 --> 00:39:38,550
Fine.

934
00:39:38,770 --> 00:39:39,330
You are right.

935
00:39:39,420 --> 00:39:40,300
You are totally right.

936
00:39:41,780 --> 00:39:42,660
How about this?

937
00:39:43,220 --> 00:39:44,640
Then let's each take a step back.

938
00:39:46,570 --> 00:39:47,710
A negotiation

939
00:39:47,890 --> 00:39:48,890
needs to have some conditions.

940
00:39:48,980 --> 00:39:49,910
Right?

941
00:39:50,770 --> 00:39:51,610
Go ahead.

942
00:39:51,700 --> 00:39:52,580
What conditions?

943
00:39:55,860 --> 00:39:56,740
Look.

944
00:39:57,540 --> 00:39:59,530
We had our winter holiday so early.

945
00:39:59,620 --> 00:40:01,080
We need to cherish it.

946
00:40:01,260 --> 00:40:02,530
Let's play for twenty days

947
00:40:02,620 --> 00:40:04,850
and I promise I will study
hard the rest of the time.

948
00:40:04,940 --> 00:40:05,880
What do you think?

949
00:40:06,100 --> 00:40:06,980
No.

950
00:40:08,180 --> 00:40:09,430
Can you promise you will not leave?

951
00:40:09,520 --> 00:40:10,920
Will you not go back and go abroad?

952
00:40:12,420 --> 00:40:12,970
No.

953
00:40:13,060 --> 00:40:14,360
That's right.

954
00:40:15,020 --> 00:40:16,210
What if one day

955
00:40:16,290 --> 00:40:17,490
your mother asks you to leave

956
00:40:17,580 --> 00:40:18,390
and I can't see you anymore?

957
00:40:18,480 --> 00:40:19,560
What can I do?

958
00:40:20,200 --> 00:40:22,200
In the future, as long as I
think about the present day,

959
00:40:22,380 --> 00:40:24,600
I can only remember
you forced me to study.

960
00:40:24,820 --> 00:40:27,120
It's not a beautiful memory.

961
00:40:33,280 --> 00:40:34,780
Hua.

962
00:40:35,090 --> 00:40:38,250
You didn't have many friends in the south.

963
00:40:38,340 --> 00:40:40,520
And you rarely come back.

964
00:40:41,140 --> 00:40:43,760
I just want to spend more time with you.

965
00:40:44,380 --> 00:40:46,390
Let's have a good winter holiday together

966
00:40:46,480 --> 00:40:48,050
with a lot of fun.

967
00:40:48,140 --> 00:40:49,950
In this way, even though
we can not meet in the future

968
00:40:50,260 --> 00:40:52,840
we still have a beautiful memory.

969
00:40:55,340 --> 00:40:57,600
Do you really want to
spend the winter holiday with me?

970
00:41:01,000 --> 00:41:02,290
Then...

971
00:41:02,380 --> 00:41:03,360
make it fifteen days.

972
00:41:03,740 --> 00:41:04,330
Eighteen days.

973
00:41:04,420 --> 00:41:05,300
Ten days.

974
00:41:05,620 --> 00:41:06,130
Why are you getting less and less?

975
00:41:06,220 --> 00:41:07,090
If you say one more
word, it will be five days.

976
00:41:07,180 --> 00:41:07,680
Fine.

977
00:41:07,770 --> 00:41:08,530
Fifteen days is ok.

978
00:41:08,620 --> 00:41:09,550
A deal!

979
00:41:10,410 --> 00:41:11,440
Du.

980
00:41:12,170 --> 00:41:13,050
What's up?

981
00:41:13,170 --> 00:41:14,490
Let's go out and play in the snow!

982
00:41:14,580 --> 00:41:15,130
Ok.

983
00:41:15,220 --> 00:41:16,120
I'll arrange it.

984
00:41:37,660 --> 00:41:38,950
Are you ready?

985
00:41:39,320 --> 00:41:40,200
Come on!

986
00:41:40,960 --> 00:41:41,840
Wait a minute.

987
00:41:42,300 --> 00:41:43,810
Why am I the only one pulling a fatty?

988
00:41:43,900 --> 00:41:44,690
She's heavier than I am.

989
00:41:44,780 --> 00:41:46,010
She should pull me.

990
00:41:46,100 --> 00:41:47,290
You have no shame!

991
00:41:47,380 --> 00:41:48,970
I can pull you. Will you sit?

992
00:41:49,050 --> 00:41:49,770
I will.

993
00:41:49,860 --> 00:41:50,690
You stand up.

994
00:41:50,780 --> 00:41:51,660
Hurry up.

995
00:41:52,130 --> 00:41:53,010
Stop arguing.

996
00:41:53,100 --> 00:41:53,610
Come on.

997
00:41:53,700 --> 00:41:54,810
The loser buys the winner barbecue.

998
00:41:54,900 --> 00:41:55,130
Come on.

999
00:41:55,210 --> 00:41:56,420
Come, ready...

1000
00:41:56,510 --> 00:41:57,450
Hurry up!

1001
00:41:57,540 --> 00:41:57,790
Three.

1002
00:41:57,880 --> 00:41:58,270
But...

1003
00:41:58,360 --> 00:41:58,910
Two.

1004
00:41:59,000 --> 00:41:59,630
One.

1005
00:41:59,710 --> 00:42:01,110
Go!

1006
00:42:07,780 --> 00:42:08,490
What's wrong?

1007
00:42:08,580 --> 00:42:10,200
Tired at the beginning?

1008
00:42:11,880 --> 00:42:12,730
Come on,

1009
00:42:12,810 --> 00:42:13,950
What is your weight?

1010
00:42:14,040 --> 00:42:15,810
Can't you slide by yourself?

1011
00:42:15,890 --> 00:42:17,530
You can't pull. But you can push.

1012
00:42:17,620 --> 00:42:18,760
Are you blaming me?

1013
00:42:18,850 --> 00:42:20,560
They have gone to the front.

1014
00:42:23,740 --> 00:42:24,620
Come on!

1015
00:42:27,860 --> 00:42:29,190
Come on, Da Mao!

1016
00:42:29,960 --> 00:42:30,730
Come on, come on, come on!

1017
00:42:30,820 --> 00:42:33,150
Surpass them!

1018
00:42:34,050 --> 00:42:36,330
Come on! They are ahead of us!

1019
00:42:36,420 --> 00:42:37,990
Shut up.

1020
00:42:53,020 --> 00:42:53,890
Don't bother me. I am annoyed.

1021
00:42:53,980 --> 00:42:55,120
Have a look.

1022
00:42:57,180 --> 00:42:58,060
Look!

1023
00:43:01,100 --> 00:43:02,040
What's that?

1024
00:43:03,500 --> 00:43:04,250
It's you.

1025
00:43:04,340 --> 00:43:06,270
Tall, handsome and strong.

1026
00:43:06,360 --> 00:43:06,970
Bro,

1027
00:43:07,050 --> 00:43:08,600
we have caused a lot
of trouble for you before.

1028
00:43:08,690 --> 00:43:09,880
Don't take it to heart.

1029
00:43:10,000 --> 00:43:11,520
We three, in the
No.3 Middle School of Tieyuan

1030
00:43:11,720 --> 00:43:12,530
share not only our joys

1031
00:43:12,620 --> 00:43:13,570
but also our sorrows.

1032
00:43:13,650 --> 00:43:15,560
This is the proof of our brotherhood.

1033
00:43:16,260 --> 00:43:16,910
I say,

1034
00:43:17,000 --> 00:43:18,560
are you three years old?

1035
00:43:18,700 --> 00:43:20,200
Shame on you! Hurry up and tear it down!

1036
00:43:20,540 --> 00:43:22,040
What's up?

1037
00:43:22,300 --> 00:43:23,890
That's what they do in Korean dramas.

1038
00:43:23,980 --> 00:43:26,160
Feelings are expressed
by building a snowman.

1039
00:43:29,610 --> 00:43:30,490
Move over!

1040
00:43:32,940 --> 00:43:34,600
Don't you have eyes?

1041
00:43:37,820 --> 00:43:39,270
It's you guys again.

1042
00:43:39,880 --> 00:43:40,920
What a coincidence. Hi.

1043
00:43:41,050 --> 00:43:42,050
We didn't mean to.

1044
00:43:42,140 --> 00:43:43,680
I can't stop the car.

1045
00:43:43,940 --> 00:43:45,480
Didn't you mean to?

1046
00:43:45,990 --> 00:43:46,970
I have said we didn't mean to.

1047
00:43:47,060 --> 00:43:48,050
What are you going to do?

1048
00:43:48,140 --> 00:43:49,110
Fan Shui Shui.

1049
00:43:49,190 --> 00:43:49,750
Li Qing Tong.

1050
00:43:49,840 --> 00:43:50,720
What's up?

1051
00:43:51,260 --> 00:43:52,140
What's up?

1052
00:43:53,050 --> 00:43:54,590
You're looking for trouble, aren't you?

1053
00:43:54,900 --> 00:43:56,280
Are we afraid of you?

1054
00:43:56,980 --> 00:43:57,630
Ok.

1055
00:43:57,720 --> 00:43:58,440
Boys stay.

1056
00:43:58,530 --> 00:44:00,240
Girls go away.

1057
00:44:00,410 --> 00:44:01,170
What are you going to do?

1058
00:44:01,260 --> 00:44:02,090
Let's go away.

1059
00:44:02,170 --> 00:44:02,890
Go.

1060
00:44:02,980 --> 00:44:03,650
OK, ok, ok.

1061
00:44:03,740 --> 00:44:05,720
Listen to him. He has bad manners.

1062
00:44:06,890 --> 00:44:08,110
Don't, don't. Wait a minute!

1063
00:44:08,540 --> 00:44:09,960
Do you know how to speak politely?

1064
00:44:15,660 --> 00:44:16,840
Didn't we make up?
